Modifications made by edronald7:
- Added dynamic region support via REGION_NAME property (AbstractS3Processor)
- Added S3-compatible endpoint support for OCI, MinIO, Cloudflare R2 and others
- Renamed processors with Universal suffix (ListS3Universal, FetchS3ObjectUniversal,
  PutS3ObjectUniversal, DeleteS3ObjectUniversal, TagS3ObjectUniversal)
- Added Use Path Style Access and Use Chunked Encoding to all five processors
- Generalized signing region extraction regex to support city-based region names
